<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>I am a Mid Software Engineer, living in Atlanta Georgia.</p>
    <p>
      I have used several different technologies to solve problems, but I tend to gravitate towards Ruby.
      I have done a few freelance mobile development jobs as a hobby using RubyMotion and Flutter.
    </p>
    <p>Follow me on <a href="https://github.com/jeremiahlukus/">Github</a> to see what I am up to.</p>

  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Things I Have Written</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b, %d") %></p>
    <% end %>

  </div>
  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I Have Built</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b, %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
